{"tid":1833000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺連登放負po同支那官媒真係合作無間","createTime":"2020-01-21T14:29:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T09:25:25.000Z","uid":231583,"like":66,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"6fd7d1ff6a9ad0c419e19c4099b9db61258a4194","tid":1833000,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T14:29:47.000Z","msg":"利申，唔係話放負po或者勇武退出po就係鬼，但失敗撚同五毛就最鍾意有呢d po，一見到就會群起入去留言放風，大家可以注意下。呢類po通常都會加句唔係放負、面對事實，再唔係就加句光復香港時代革命五大訴求缺一不可，hea撚過燉炳強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>快過年了，&ldquo;亂港&rdquo;分子卻深深陷入絕望。</strong> - 新民周刊 2020-01-21 15:20:27<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>精彩節錄：<br />\n<blockquote>在街頭，擺明了是看熱鬧的人多，包括懷有各種目的的各路記者或者所謂的&ldquo;記者&rdquo;，都不少。然而，站在第一線搞事者卻越來越少！這恰恰印證了香港一些縱暴網站上的傳聞。<span style=\"color: red;\">此前，&ldquo;連登&rdquo;論壇裡就流露出一些&ldquo;勇武派&rdquo;宣布退場的消息。</span></blockquote><br />\n有暴徒在網上發帖詢問&ldquo;同夥&rdquo;：&ldquo;覺不覺得身邊很多人已經開始重新正常生活？&rdquo;<br />\n在帖文下面，有人留言稱，身邊不少人已經繼續按部就班籌備買房、努力上班，之前都會出來游行集會，但最近都沒有出來了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://junshi-pic.china.com/202001/21/1579590973_20833200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjunshi-pic.china.com%2F202001%2F21%2F1579590973_20833200.jpg&h=35ac1027&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">香港明面上的暴徒數量在減少的同時，所謂&ldquo;黃色經濟圈&rdquo;的論調甚囂塵上</span>，這不，&ldquo;亂港&rdquo;分子趁著春節將至，還要號召香港市民罷看&ldquo;中資賀歲片&rdquo;。</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">大家開po或者睇po留言既時候，請多多注意同提防，我地新一年繼續不分化，睇完不妨幫手推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"18dc987caf66a5b2cb287dba9ffb75ad38364550","tid":1833000,"uid":256181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T14:30:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d736fe79efb555f87872048050b2becfdacd0b19","tid":1833000,"uid":231583,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T14:30:13.000Z","msg":"btw仲有個重點，佢地又反黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38436e8da4c9ad7701958c441c86d0947dd7d82e","tid":1833000,"uid":231583,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d736fe79efb555f87872048050b2becfdacd0b19","tid":1833000,"uid":231583,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T14:30:13.000Z","msg":"btw仲有個重點，佢地又反黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T14:30:53.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;亂港&rdquo;分子趁著春節將至，還要號召香港市民罷看&ldquo;中資賀歲片&rdquo;。包括林超賢執導的《緊急救援》、陳可辛導演的《奪冠》，以及《哪吒之魔童降世》。"},{"pid":"5b10eec0ccf28b3084b549badd8376f447c87842","tid":1833000,"uid":256181,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T14:30:58.000Z","msg":"保持獨立思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ba81715a91a51d1e9f2b051f486b1976140164","tid":1833000,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5b10eec0ccf28b3084b549badd8376f447c87842","tid":1833000,"uid":256181,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T14:30:58.000Z","msg":"保持獨立思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T14:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea02048909205811bc12c20d303fb1648052cd8e","tid":1833000,"uid":256181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T14:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d450a28e9f67f3dc9b65920d8098a0cdec9e21a7","tid":1833000,"uid":199292,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T14:32:16.000Z","msg":"其實入面有啲真係手足嚟 <br />\n但帶放負方向嘅人加劇左個情況"},{"pid":"449201b2b5eb75cddb0594659b487e5724e625e9","tid":1833000,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB